@startuml IRouter_swapSingleTokenExactIn
actor User
participant Router
participant Vault
participant Pool
participant Hooks

== Initiation ==
User -> Router: swapSingleTokenExactIn(pool, tokenIn, tokenOut, exactAmountIn, minAmountOut, deadline, wethIsEth, userData)
note right: User calls Router to swap exact amount of tokenIn for tokenOut.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L429-L450

== Vault Unlocking ==
Router -> Vault: unlock(params)
note right: Router encodes SwapSingleTokenHookParams and calls Vault.unlock.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L435-L449\n**Code Citation (Vault)**: Vault.sol#L191-L197

== Swap Single Token Hook ==
Vault -> Router: swapSingleTokenHook(params)
note right: Vault executes Router's swapSingleTokenHook.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L581-L602

== Swap Logic ==
Router -> Vault: swap(VaultSwapParams with kind=EXACT_IN)
note right: Router calls Vault.swap to compute swap amounts.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L583-L592\n**Code Citation (Vault)**: Vault.sol#L258-L346

alt shouldCallBeforeSwap == true
    Vault -> Hooks: onBeforeSwap(swapParams, pool)
    note right: Vault calls hook (if enabled) for pre-swap logic.\n**Code Citation (Hooks)**: HooksConfigLib.sol#L170-L179
    Hooks --> Vault: true
    note right: Hook returns true, signaling success.\n**Code Citation (Hooks)**: HooksConfigLib.sol#L175
end alt

Vault -> Pool: onSwap(swapParams)
note right: Vault calls pool's onSwap to compute amountOut.\n**Code Citation (Pool)**: IBasePool.sol#L67-L70\n**Code Citation (Vault)**: Vault.sol#L313-L315

alt shouldCallAfterSwap == true
    Vault -> Hooks: onAfterSwap(afterSwapParams)
    note right: Vault calls hook (if enabled) for post-swap logic.\nMay adjust amountCalculated if enableHookAdjustedAmounts is true.\n**Code Citation (Hooks)**: HooksConfigLib.sol#L192-L215
    Hooks --> Vault: adjustedAmountCalculatedRaw
    note right: Hook returns adjusted amount if applicable.\n**Code Citation (Hooks)**: HooksConfigLib.sol#L210
end alt

Vault --> Router: amountCalculated, amountIn, amountOut

== Token Transfers ==
Router -> Vault: takeTokenIn(sender, tokenIn, amountIn, wethIsEth)
note right: Router handles tokenIn transfer, including WETH wrapping if needed.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L595-L597

Router -> Vault: sendTokenOut(sender, tokenOut, amountOut, wethIsEth)
note right: Router handles tokenOut transfer, including WETH unwrapping if needed.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L598-L600

== Vault Settlement ==
Vault -> Vault: check _tokenDeltas == 0
note right: Vault ensures all transient debts are settled.\n**Code Citation (Vault)**: Vault.sol#L167-L189

== Router Finalization ==
Router -> User: amountOut
note right: Router returns the amount of tokenOut received.\n**Code Citation**: Router.sol#L450

@enduml